{"ID":"20220906204329-hxmexu5","Spec":"1","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"id":"20220906204329-hxmexu5","title":"g-1网关","type":"doc","updated":"20220906204329"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906204330-6vuu3y5","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20220906204330-6vuu3y5","updated":"20220906204330"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"## ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"7.2 网关","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204331-w4u73cl","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20220906204331-w4u73cl","updated":"20220906204331"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"### ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"何为网关？为什么要网关？","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204332-0spuj70","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204332-0spuj70","updated":"20220906204332"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"微服务背景下，一个系统被拆分为多个服务，但是像安全认证，流量控制，日志，监控等功能是每个服务都需要的，没有网关的话，我们就需要在每个服务中单独实现，这使得我们做了很多重复的事情并且没有一个全局的视图来统一管理这些功能。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204333-q8vc59h","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204333-q8vc59h","updated":"20220906204333"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Properties":{"id":""},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang","Data":"!","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket","Data":"[","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"网关示意图","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket","Data":"]","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen","Data":"(","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"https://guide-blog-images.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/github/javaguide/system-design/distributed-system/api-gateway-overview.png","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen","Data":")","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906204334-68kwks3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204334-68kwks3","updated":"20220906204334"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"一般情况下，网关可以为我们提供请求转发、安全认证（身份/权限认证）、流量控制、负载均衡、降级熔断、日志、监控等功能。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204335-rdno8zg","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204335-rdno8zg","updated":"20220906204335"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"上面介绍了这么多功能，实际上，网关主要做了一件事情：","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"请求过滤"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204336-hzr7n8z","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20220906204336-hzr7n8z","updated":"20220906204336"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"### ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"有哪些常见的网关系统？","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204337-q0xlsdl","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20220906204337-q0xlsdl","updated":"20220906204337"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"#### ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"Netflix Zuul","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204338-4joobf3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204338-4joobf3","updated":"20220906204338"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"Zuul 是 Netflix 开发的一款提供动态路由、监控、弹性、安全的网关服务。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204339-amghgna","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204339-amghgna","updated":"20220906204339"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"Zuul 主要通过过滤器（类似于 AOP）来过滤请求，从而实现网关必备的各种功能。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204340-bjdilpp","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204340-bjdilpp","updated":"20220906204340"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Properties":{"id":""},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang","Data":"!","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket","Data":"[","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"Zuul架构","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket","Data":"]","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen","Data":"(","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/img_convert/865991e34f69f8cb345b4aff918e946e.png","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen","Data":")","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906204341-ygqom2w","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204341-ygqom2w","updated":"20220906204341"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"我们可以自定义过滤器来处理请求，并且，Zuul 生态本身就有很多现成的过滤器供我们使用。就比如限流可以直接用国外朋友写的 ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"a","TextMarkAHref":"https://github.com/marcosbarbero/spring-cloud-zuul-ratelimit","TextMarkTextContent":"spring-cloud-zuul-ratelimit"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" (这里只是举例说明，一般是配合 hystrix 来做限流)：","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204342-mtr2mh3","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"CodeBlockFenceChar":96,"CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"CodeBlockOpenFence":"YGBg","CodeBlockInfo":"eG1s","CodeBlockCloseFence":"YGBg","Properties":{"id":"20220906204342-mtr2mh3","updated":"20220906204342"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"eG1s","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"\u003cdependency\u003e\n  \u003cgroupId\u003eorg.springframework.cloud\u003c/groupId\u003e\n    \u003cartifactId\u003espring-cloud-starter-netflix-zuul\u003c/artifactId\u003e\n\u003c/dependency\u003e\n\u003cdependency\u003e\n    \u003cgroupId\u003ecom.marcosbarbero.cloud\u003c/groupId\u003e\n    \u003cartifactId\u003espring-cloud-zuul-ratelimit\u003c/artifactId\u003e\n    \u003cversion\u003e2.2.0.RELEASE\u003c/version\u003e\n\u003c/dependency\u003e\n","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204343-65f9yla","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204343-65f9yla","updated":"20220906204343"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"Zuul 1.x 基于同步 IO，性能较差。Zuul 2.x 基于 Netty 实现了异步 IO，性能得到了大幅改进。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204344-yscpunn","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906204344-yscpunn","updated":"20220906204344"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906204345-g9a3u47","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906204345-g9a3u47","updated":"20220906204345"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906204346-mswj7zy","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204346-mswj7zy","updated":"20220906204346"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"Github 地址 ： https://github.com/Netflix/zuul","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906204347-ih3slf5","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906204347-ih3slf5","updated":"20220906204347"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906204348-43zqpk6","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204348-43zqpk6","updated":"20220906204348"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"官方 Wiki ： https://github.com/Netflix/zuul/wiki","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]}]},{"ID":"20220906204349-nwe5kqo","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20220906204349-nwe5kqo","updated":"20220906204349"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"#### ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"Spring Cloud Gateway","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204350-8ak4g35","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204350-8ak4g35","updated":"20220906204350"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"SpringCloud Gateway 属于 Spring Cloud 生态系统中的网关，其诞生的目标是为了替代老牌网关 **Zuul **。准确点来说，应该是 Zuul 1.x。SpringCloud Gateway 起步要比 Zuul 2.x 更早。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204351-t4q9i47","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204351-t4q9i47","updated":"20220906204351"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"为了提升网关的性能，SpringCloud Gateway 基于 Spring WebFlux 。Spring WebFlux 使用 Reactor 库来实现响应式编程模型，底层基于 Netty 实现异步 IO。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204352-qkseciw","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204352-qkseciw","updated":"20220906204352"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"Spring Cloud Gateway 的目标，不仅提供统一的路由方式，并且基于 Filter 链的方式提供了网关基本的功能，例如：安全，监控/指标，和限流。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204353-gpzpx8b","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204353-gpzpx8b","updated":"20220906204353"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"Spring Cloud Gateway 和 Zuul 2.x 的差别不大，也是通过过滤器来处理请求。不过，目前更加推荐使用 Spring Cloud Gateway 而非 Zuul，Spring Cloud 生态对其支持更加友好。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204354-qc2ofvk","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906204354-qc2ofvk","updated":"20220906204354"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906204355-d5fxj4k","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906204355-d5fxj4k","updated":"20220906204355"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906204356-ym4he7w","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204356-ym4he7w","updated":"20220906204356"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"Github 地址 ： https://github.com/spring-cloud/spring-cloud-gateway","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906204357-g7evaxg","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906204357-g7evaxg","updated":"20220906204357"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906204358-tmr6nql","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204358-tmr6nql","updated":"20220906204358"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"官网 ： https://spring.io/projects/spring-cloud-gateway","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]}]},{"ID":"20220906204359-d7kayjk","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20220906204359-d7kayjk","updated":"20220906204359"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"#### ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"Kong","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204360-8mnxdfh","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204360-8mnxdfh","updated":"20220906204360"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"Kong 是一款基于 ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"a","TextMarkAHref":"https://github.com/openresty/","TextMarkTextContent":"OpenResty"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 的高性能、云原生、可扩展的网关系统。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204361-vymto00","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20220906204361-vymto00","updated":"20220906204361"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"ID":"20220906204362-jfv5r0i","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204362-jfv5r0i","updated":"20220906204362"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"OpenResty 是一个基于 Nginx 与 Lua 的高性能 Web 平台，其内部集成了大量精良的 Lua 库、第三方模块以及大多数的依赖项。用于方便地搭建能够处理超高并发、扩展性极高的动态 Web 应用、Web 服务和动态网关。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906204363-wkm0rey","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204363-wkm0rey","updated":"20220906204363"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"Kong 提供了插件机制来扩展其功能。比如、在服务上启用 Zipkin 插件","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204364-s3jo0ht","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"CodeBlockFenceChar":96,"CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"CodeBlockOpenFence":"YGBg","CodeBlockInfo":"c2hlbGw=","CodeBlockCloseFence":"YGBg","Properties":{"id":"20220906204364-s3jo0ht","updated":"20220906204364"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"c2hlbGw=","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"$ curl -X POST http://kong:8001/services/{service}/plugins \\\n    --data \"name=zipkin\"  \\\n    --data \"config.http_endpoint=http://your.zipkin.collector:9411/api/v2/spans\" \\\n    --data \"config.sample_ratio=0.001\"\n","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204365-3npsixt","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906204365-3npsixt","updated":"20220906204365"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906204366-5qe5crg","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906204366-5qe5crg","updated":"20220906204366"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906204367-3mxg6pf","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204367-3mxg6pf","updated":"20220906204367"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"Github 地址： https://github.com/Kong/kong","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906204368-mq42kwh","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906204368-mq42kwh","updated":"20220906204368"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906204369-3fomd2t","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204369-3fomd2t","updated":"20220906204369"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"官网地址 ： https://konghq.com/kong","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]}]},{"ID":"20220906204370-gbgdk66","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20220906204370-gbgdk66","updated":"20220906204370"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"#### ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"APISIX","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204371-igwxskk","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204371-igwxskk","updated":"20220906204371"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"APISIX 是一款基于 Nginx 和 etcd 的高性能、云原生、可扩展的网关系统。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204372-y1vebmc","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20220906204372-y1vebmc","updated":"20220906204372"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"ID":"20220906204373-x5x887v","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204373-x5x887v","updated":"20220906204373"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"em","TextMarkTextContent":"etcd"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"是使用 Go 语言开发的一个开源的、高可用的分布式 key-value 存储系统，使用 Raft 协议做分布式共识。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906204374-vxwxhpr","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204374-vxwxhpr","updated":"20220906204374"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"与传统 API 网关相比，APISIX 具有动态路由和插件热加载，特别适合微服务系统下的 API 管理。并且，APISIX 与 SkyWalking（分布式链路追踪系统）、Zipkin（分布式链路追踪系统）、Prometheus（监控系统） 等 DevOps 生态工具对接都十分方便。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204375-n3xlax0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204375-n3xlax0","updated":"20220906204375"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Properties":{"id":""},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang","Data":"!","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket","Data":"[","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"apisix架构图","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket","Data":"]","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen","Data":"(","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/img_convert/727732fad2e943bdd2c502b83ddb1b89.png","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen","Data":")","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906204376-263bumt","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204376-263bumt","updated":"20220906204376"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"作为 NGINX 和 Kong 的替代项目，APISIX 目前已经是 Apache 顶级开源项目，并且是最快毕业的国产开源项目。国内目前已经有很多知名企业（比如金山、有赞、爱奇艺、腾讯、贝壳）使用 APISIX 处理核心的业务流量。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204377-5jo5wke","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204377-5jo5wke","updated":"20220906204377"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"根据官网介绍：“APISIX 已经生产可用，功能、性能、架构全面优于 Kong”。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204378-cw8uina","Type":"NodeLis